description:
Axie Infinity is an open-ended game universe full of fierce, adorable pets called Axies. Players aim to battle, breed, collect, raise, and build kingdoms for their Axies across Lunacia, the Axie homeland. Lunacia is divided into tokenized plots of land which act as home bases for Axies.

Axies vary in countless unique body parts and appearances. Body parts unlock abilities for Axies, giving them special benefits and skills from one game to another. Resources spawn in nodes across Lunacia and can be used to upgrade both land and Axies.
title: AXIE

description: 10,000 unique collectible characters with proof of ownership stored on the Ethereum blockchain. The project that inspired the modern CryptoArt movement. An inspiration for the Ethereum ERC-721 standard that powers most digital art and collectibles. No two punks are alike, and each one of them can be officially owned by a single person on the Ethereum blockchain. Originally, they could be claimed for free by anybody with an Ethereum wallet, but all 10,000 were quickly claimed. Now they must be purchased from someone on the Ethereum marketplace contract. Via the market, you can buy, bid on, and offer punks for sale.
title: CryptoPunks

description:
Storefront for genuinely programmable and on-demand generative artwork that is stored directly on the Ethereum blockchain. Pick your style and mint! Each piece is randomly generated by an algorithm defined by the artist, there are endless possibilities to what your unique generation could look like.

A generative script (p5js, for example) is stored on the Ethereum blockchain for each project launched on Art Blocks. Using an initial unique “seed,” you can be sure that every iteration is random, generative, and one-of-a-kind.
title: Art Blocks

description:
Otherside is a gamified, interoperable metaverse currently under development by Yuga Labs. Players will own the world, NFTs can become playable characters, and thousands will be able to play together in real time.

Every Otherdeed is a dynamic NFT, built as a collection of all of its elements, from resources to Kodas — the primal beings that have ushered us into the Otherside. Land owners can participate in demos, prototypes, and test builds that shape the final game design and experience.

Where the swamp ends, the Otherside begins.
title: Otherdeed

description:
Loot is randomized adventurer gear generated and stored on chain. Stats, images, and other functionality are intentionally omitted for others to interpret.

Each loot bag contains 8 items: a piece for an adventurers chest, foot, hand, head, neck, ring, waist, and weapon.
title: Loot

description:
Azuki is a collection of anime style avatars that grant membership access to The Garden. The Garden is a corner of the internet where art, community, and culture fuse to create magic. The lines between physical and digital worlds are blurring and the rules are being rewritten.

BEANZ are small species that sprout from the dirt in the garden. Some BEANZ make great sidekicks, but others enjoy kicking it alone.
title: Azuki

description:
CloneX Corp was founded by three extraterrestrials who came from the planet of Orbitar in the Draco constellation. These interplanetary tourists have come to accelerate our evolution towards an immaterial existence. They plan to transfer all human consciousness into advanced clone forms to create the ultimate metaverse.

In this advanced civilization, humans no longer reside in an organic form but are instead represented by their digital CloneX avatars. This ground breaking technology has revolutionized Homo sapiens’ ability to self-express themselves through customizable avatar identities. This development also allows clones to travel across galaxies and expand our civilization into new galaxies and simulations.

By RTFKT Studios and Takashi Murakami.
title: CloneX

description:
Moonbirds is the continuation and evolution of the PROOF project, led by PROOF Collective. This collection represents 10,000 owls randomly generated on the Ethereum blockchain with a pixel art design.

Owning a Moonbird grants the holder access to the metaverse of PROOF, Project Highrise.

description:
Cool Cats are the coolest cats on the blockchain. The first generation consists of 9,999 randomly assembled cats, each comprised of a unique body, hat, face, and outfit. All are cool, but everyone has their favorite — what’s yours?

Cool Pets are the cool, cute companions to Cool Cats. There are a total of 19,999 Cool Pets, waiting to be evolved into their final forms. From little tasks to epic adventures, Cool Pets can go on quests to help Sapphire Town and Cooltopia.

Audioglyphs is a collection of 10,000 randomly generated, infinite audio NFTs derived from on-chain Pixelglyph data. Corresponding Audioglyphs and Pixelglyphs can be found by matching asset IDs.

Each Audioglyph synthesizes a unique, infinite stream of music directly in your browser at lossless quality.

VeeFriends is a Gary Vaynerchuk NFT project around meaningful intellectual property and an extraordinary community. The inaugural collection features 10,255 VeeFriends tokens. The collection focuses on human traits that Gary most admires, and believes will lead to happiness and success.

The original VeeFriends characters have now evolved into their life-like Series 2 form as the VeeFriends universe takes shape. Series 2 features 15 brand new characters.

VeeFriends Mini Drops (VFMD) are surprise drops for the VeeFriends community.

description: Secure and decentralized name service for both on and off-chain resources using simple, human-readable names. ENS eliminates the need to use long and illegible wallet addresses on Ethereum, Bitcoin and other blockchains. First in it’s class, supported by over 100 wallets and applications, ENS is paving the road for Ethereum usability.
title: Ethereum Name Service

description:
Nouns are 32×32 pixel generative NFT characters based on people, places, and things. They are an experimental attempt to improve the formation of on-chain avatar communities. Nouns attempt to bootstrap identity, community, governance, and a treasury that can be used by the community.

One noun is generated every day. One noun is also auctioned every 24 hours, forever.
title: Nouns

description: World of Women was created with the aim of bringing more diversity and representation into the NFT space. The original collection features 10,000 unique, cool, and diverse women. description: Decentraland is a virtual reality platform powered by the Ethereum blockchain. Users can create, experience, and monetize content and applications. LAND in Decentraland is permanently owned by the community, giving them full control over their creations. Users claim ownership of virtual land on a blockchain-based ledger of parcels. Landowners control what content is published to their portion of land, which is identified by a set of cartesian coordinates (x,y). Contents can range from static 3D scenes to interactive experiences such as games.
title: Land

LAND in Decentraland is permanently owned by the community, giving them full control over their creations. Users claim ownership of virtual land on a blockchain-based ledger of parcels. Landowners control what content is published to their portion of land, which is identified by a set of cartesian coordinates (x,y). Contents can range from static 3D scenes to interactive experiences such as games.

The MekaVerse is a collection of 8,888 generative Mekas with hundreds of elements inspired by the Japan Mecha universes.

Each artwork is original, with its own color palette and creation. The objective was to make each Meka unique in order to prioritize quality above quantity.
title: MekaVerse

description:
Life in the ethereal enclave was peaceful and prosperous. Rule under the emperor granted eternal life, infinite leisure for music, arts and poetry. For many this was bliss, but when the emperor suddenly died without an heir, everything collapsed.

What was once everlasting has now been considered to a mere 7 777 hours. Now, gathering means for survival as society crumbles, the 0n1 face their greatest enemies: themselves
title: 0n1force

description:
FLUFs have been programmatically generated from 270 attributes across 14 categories to be entirely unique by at least three degrees of separation. This also excludes their expression, dance, scene, and soundtrack.

description:
The Circuits of Value (COVAL) Emblem Vault protocol introduces the ability to combine tokens from different blockchains into a single ERC-721 token. This newly-created token container, or vault, is now a multi-asset crypto wallet in the form of a tradable NFT.

With Emblem Vaults you can create value-backed digital assets, tradable portfolios, portable liquidity pools, and more.

description:
Nifty Gateway is the premier marketplace for Nifties, which are digital items you can truly own. Nifty Gateway is also a centralized, USD-based marketplace for buying and selling Nifties. Nifty Gateway lets you display your Nifties, as well as withdraw them to external wallets, or deposit Nifties from external wallets into your collection.

IMPORTANT NOTE: NONFUNGIBLE.COM IS CURRENTLY INDEXING ETHEREUM ON-CHAIN SALES. NIFTYGATEWAY IS KNOWN TO PERFORM MOST OF THEIR VOLUME OFF-CHAIN, THIS MAY CAUSE SOME MARKET HISTORY AND STATISTICS TO BE MISSING OR LESS THAN THEIR ACTUAL VALUE.
title: niftygateway

description: Hashmasks is part CryptoArt collectible, part token mining, and part utility. The design of each individual layer has been hand-crafted by one of over 70 different artist in this mega-collaboration. While holding Hashmasks pays you in their native fungible token, “NCT” (Name change token), these tokens allow you to change the name of your mask when burned.

description:
Art Gobblers is an experimental decentralized art factory by Justin Roiland and Paradigm. Each Art Gobbler functions as a fully animated NFT art gallery, where gobbled art pages become a permanent part of that Gobbler’s belly gallery. Art Gobblers produce Goo tokens, which are used to produce the blank pages needed to make art. The more Goo a Gobbler has, the faster it generates more Goo.

A total supply of 2,000 Art Gobblers will initially exist. Goo will be used to teleport new Art Gobblers down to Earth until the remaining 8,000 Gobblers are minted. The ten Legendary Gobblers are extravagantly rare one-of-one Gobblers that represent the supreme rulers of Gobbler civilization.

The invasion has begun! Feed the Art Gobblers your art and help them cover the world in Goo.
title: Art Gobblers

The Currency by Damien Hirst is a collection of 10,000 NFTs, each corresponding to an original work on paper stored in a secure vault in the UK. The collector has to decide between the digital NFT or the physical artwork, but can not keep both…the other gets burned.

The titles are generated from machine learning being applied to some of the artist’s favorite song lyrics. All of the different identifying features of each work have been analyzed and ranked out of 10,000. From the amount of drips and splashes, to the texture of the paint, each artwork has a unique combination of ranked features.
title: The Currency

description:
An early crypto art project about the nature of the artwork-as-a-token. The Digital Zones digitally reproduce Yves Klein’s invisible artworks, and tell a story about how different concepts of ownership are fundamental to the experience of an artwork.

The artwork is significant not only for being one of the earliest NFT artworks to be exhibited and minted in a legacy art gallery, but also for imagining, in 2017, the ways that non-fungible tokens could advance the conceptualist project of separating the commodity form of an artwork from the experienced form. It also explored the ways the separation changes a collector’s relationship to art.

IKB Cachet de Garantie is a wrapper for the original IKB token, which deployed August 30, 2017.
title: IKB Cachet de Garantie

Ownership includes full commercial and creative rights to your JYD, as well as access to our exclusive merch, community events, and games.
title: JunkYard Dogs

description: Gossamer World is a large-scale Web 3 project being created by Hollywood studio BRON. Each warrior provides exclusive access to a world overlapping with Web 3, TV, and a AAA game franchise. Gossamer NFTs also provide first-access to all future BRON NFT projects.
title: Gossamer Seed

title: The Secret Society XX

description: Owning a GOAT will open the doors for you to a vibrant and thriving community filled with like-minded individuals all searching for greatness. Owning 2 or more will unlock the Forge for your GOATz. Own or Forge the GOAT you dream of becoming!
title: GOATz

description:
Solarbots is a blockchain-powered, interactive social metaverse in the form of a multi-faceted game that is both fun to play and reflective of one’s own personal search for meaning. Bravely board the fickle coin of war and peace and join the last defense of the plane of Eld. Fight back the abyssal hordes in this last stand effort!

Solarbots are the robots crafted by each faction: Arboria, Illskagaard, and the Lacrean Empire. The factions offer only visual differences, allowing players to freely choose based on whichever style they like best.
title: Solarbots

description:
7,000 Sad Frogs programmatically generated from a random combination of more than 200 traits.

The Frogs are inspired by collective artworks of internet artists and cyberpunk aesthetics.
title: Sad Frogs District

description:
The Last 10,000.

CryptoPunks were the first 10,000. CryptoZunks are the (unofficial) last 10,000.

Numbered 10,000 – 19,999, Zunks are the first Punks to be generated on-chain with randomized attributes. Each Zunk is guaranteed to be unique from any Punk. On top of that, Zunk’s attributes were able to be modified on-chain for a short window after minting – giving owner’s the power over their Zunk’s destiny.
title: CryptoZunks

description:
Weather Report is a collection of 10,000 reporters ready for all conditions. Rain or shine, they’re here.

The artwork is heavily inﬂuenced by late 1990s skateboarding culture, giving the art a very nostalgic feel of that time period.
title: Weather Report

description:
Upon arriving at their destination on Planet XOLO, the crew of the E.S.C. JOURNEY are forced to prepare themselves for a crash landing. Follow the tales and adventures of the remaining crew as they try to overcome the many obstacles they may face.

This collection of stranded villagers on Planet XOLO is the first set from JRNY Club.
title: Villagers of XOLO

description:
Bulls and Apes Project is a collection of 3D bulls. The genesis collection features 10,000 Genesis Bulls and 500 God Bulls. Each of the bulls belongs to one of four guilds.

Teen Bulls are generated by merging the DNA of two Genesis Bulls of the same guild. Four Teen Bulls of different guilds can summon a God Bull. Let the fun begin!
title: BAP Genesis & God Bulls

description:
Bulls and Apes Project is a collection of 3D bulls. The genesis collection features 10,000 Genesis Bulls and 500 God Bulls. Each of the bulls belongs to one of four guilds.

description: God Hates NFTees is a collection of 5,022 protestor NFTs in Rick & Morty style. GHN is a collection where the scoundrel, the informal, and the trolling predominate, but always with ethics.
title: God Hates NFTees

description:
GossApe Girl is a collection of 7,000 ape ladies glamorizing the Ethereum blockchain. Each GossApe Girl features meticulously hand-drawn traits, an awesome sense of fashion and confidence, and of course, a little luck via algorithmic generation. But most importantly, the GossApe Girl is on a mission to bring inclusivity, equality, and beauty to the NFT space.

GossApe Girl shifts the male ape narrative and enables access for women by introducing a feminine, fashionable, and stylish approach to the blockchain through the female ape.
title: GossApe Girl

description: Moshi Mochi is a community-driven collection of 8,000 squishy, little Mochi NFTs wandering the Ethereum blockchain. With a combination of over 100 traits, each Mochi is made to be unique and no two are alike!
title: Moshi Mochi

description:
The Chiptos NFT collections feature unique robots made out of computer parts.

Chiptos is the original collection of 512 3D-rendered, animated robots, and the first major project developed by GaperArt and Cam Taylor. Chiptos X is the next-generation collection and flagship launch of the Chiptos universe. Chiptos X is your ticket to all things Chiptos!
title: Chiptos 512

They’ve been cruising through various celestial bodies, galaxies, black holes, and stratospheres, and have noticed that their Earthling friends are ready. They were shocked to find that their ancient ancestors, the T-Rex and Spinosaurus, are extinct, and want to help repopulate the old Cretaceous forests and swamps.

With blockchain technology, users can play, earn, own, trade, and govern the League of Kingdoms universe without the ownership flaws of traditional digital games.

Peacefall is a battle-based NFT collection of 8,192 warriors hand-created by the legendary Koji Ogata, one of the artists on the original Double Dragon.

The more your character wins, the stronger they become. As your warrior evolves, its appearance will change, earning new weaponry and stronger in-game stats.

description:
As a leading hub for entrepreneurs to learn, innovate, and connect through the power of Web 3, Metapreneurs strives to close the gap between starting entrepreneurs and experienced business owners by providing real-world utility to both.

The Metapreneurs collection features 11,111 unique NFTs assembled from more than 600+ hand-drawn traits.
title: Metapreneurs

description: Polychain Monsters are beautifully animated digital collectibles with varying scarcities. Each Polychain Monster is backed by a truly unique NFT and can be unpacked with $PMON tokens.
title: Monsters

description: Solvency is a limited edition series of WebGL artworks created by Ezra Miller. Each artwork is a completely unique, randomly generated by the Solvency smart contract at the time of minting using a deterministic algorithm seeded with the hash of the token.
title: Solvency by Ezra Miller

description: Regulars is a generative profile picture collectibles project on the Ethereum blockchain. Regulars are individually rendered in 3D and brought to life with high attention to detail.
title: Regulars

description:
From the mind of American music video director, Colin Tilley, Castle Kid is a generative NFT project composed of 10,000 Castle Kid combinations. Castle Kid features hand-drawn art from Philadelphia-based graffiti and digital artist, $20,000 (20thousand).

Holders will get access to Colin Tilley through production, ideation, and imaginative masterclasses that explore the mind of an award winning creator. Be a part of the creative process as the story of Castle Kid unfolds.
title: Castle Kid

description: Hedz is a collection of 1,000 hand-drawn NFT characters from comic and illustrious creator of Pepe the Frog, Matt Furie. Each Hedz is a 1/1 work of love with a unique name.
title: Hedz

description:
6,313 unique, scifi-mythic creatures, ranging from sentient robots to immortal cosmic beings…

3D interactivity, swappable backgrounds, ambient music, and also the first NFT project to partner with The Sandbox to create playable avatars for VoxoDeus NFT owners.
title: Voxos

description:
The finiliar NFT collection features 10,000 animated characters who use oracles to respond to fluctuations in the value of cryptocurrencies. When the currency a finiliar is coupled with does well, it becomes happy and buoyant, but if the linked coin performs poorly, the finiliar can become sad or sick.

Different finiliar operate on different timeframes, some adjusting their mood every hour.
title: Finiliar

description:
Dancing Seahorse is a private members club that grants exclusive access to incredible, once in a lifetime global experiences. Their goal is to change the music industry forever.

The first Dancing Seahorse NFT collection launched in September, 2022, and features 444 Legendary Dancing Seahorses (LDS) doubling as private club memberships.
title: Legendary Dancing Seahorse

description:
The Lobstars is a collection of 7,777 unique lobster portraits by internationally renowned British artist, Philip Colbert.

Every Lobstar NFT holder is a citizen of Lobsteropolis, the ever-expanding art world of Philip Colbert.
title: The Lobstars

description: SuperYetis are 3D interactive characters randomized through a secret algorithm to ensure everyone gets a cute AF SuperYeti.
title: Yeti

description:
Blockchain Bikers is an eco-system of biker culture within the NFT world—bringing with them an entire PFP experience. As the dust settled and only one avatar could remain, the bikers took it upon themselves to equip their helmets and run the Twitter-verse with one simple saying: #rideordie.

The Blockchain Bikers NFT collection features 11,111 bikers ready to race down the Ethereum highway.
title: BlockchainBikers

description: Women Ape Yacht Club is a collection of female ape NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain launched by the 99xClub team. Meet the gorgeous women from the Women Ape Yacht Club who hope to inspire and empower women, and bring a little sizzle to the blockchain.
title: Women Ape Yacht Club

description: An Urbit ID is all you need to log into Urbit OS and will let you send and receive crypto payments. IDs come in 2 sizes: planets for personal use and stars for infrastructure to support communities.
title: Azimuth Points

description:
There are four packs with 2,000 dogs in each. Ownership includes access to the Beach Bar, real-world benefits, and complete commercial rights to your doggo.

All of the art work is hand-drawn and algorithmically generated using custom code. There are over 150 properties across 11 categories: background, body, clothes, ears, eyes, face, glasses, hats, mouths, necklaces, and noses. This gives a total mathematical combination of hundreds of thousands of unique dogs—but with only 8,000 being minted, some are more unique and rare than others.
title: Top Dog Beach Club

description: Enter ethblock.art: a multi-level collaborative conversation between creative coders, visual artists, and collectors; all occurring in one, common medium—the raw data outputs of a single, shared, global machine.
title: BlockArt

description:
These creatures have 124 completely random traits and live on the Ethereum network with ERC-721 token standard and all the data is stored on chain on IPFS making them both beautiful and immutable.

When you buy a Glue Factory NFT, you’re not just buying a piece of art or an avatar, but a collectible from a future ‘colt’ classic.
title: Glue Factory Show

description:
ETHEREALS is a collection of 12,345 hand drawn, randomly generated, interdimensional ghosts by artist, Jimmy Danko.

Their traits are pulled from all reaches of the metaverse and include surprising mashups of cultural references all the way down to super-insider rarities. They are eternal beings that travel through time and space in search of FUN!
title: ETHEREALS

XANA is a blockchain infrastructure and robust DApps platform custom-built for the metaverse.

XANA: Genesis Avatars (XGS) are your very own metaverse AI partners, and represent the first-ever original NFT collection of XANA.

3D virtual space within XANA is called LAND (XLD). LAND is divided into parcels identified by cartesian coordinates.

description:
Cheech & Chong are transporting you to Dreamland: a whimsical world just beyond our own. Dreamland is full of weird and wonderful energy, and even weirder new homies!

Homies in Dreamland is a collection of 10,420 NFTs designed by artist Jermaine Rogers, inspired by the legendary duo Cheech & Chong.
title: My Homies In Dreamland

description:
Nudie Community is a collection of 10,000 hairless cats cruising the metaverse. Many millennia ago, 10,000 Nudies left their home planet of Nudetopia to form the Nudie Community. Their goal was to explore the galaxy and help evolve civilizations that they would find along the way.

Nudie Community is a women-led, community-focused project dedicated to empowering and uplifting women in the Web3 space.
title: Nudie Community

description:
Sherbet is a social, candy-themed PvP casino built using the latest Web3 technology. Rather than gambling against the house, compete against friends and foes in a variety of original games.

The Sherbet NFT collection features 7,777 candy characters bringing you luck at the Sherbet casino. Collecting one provides various utilities, such as early access to new features, passive token earning, discounted commissions, exclusive games, chat perks, and more.
title: Sherbet

description:
Hedgies is a project by dydx that features unique, collectible avatars represented as NFTs on Ethereum.

Meet a very special group of small, spiny animals who love nothing more than trading perpetuals, are filled with references to crypto and trading, and celebrate the unique culture of Web 3.
title: Hedgies by dYdX

description:
Refik Anadol is a media artist, director, and pioneer in the aesthetics of machine intelligence. Anadol’s body of work addresses the challenges, and the possibilities, that ubiquitous computing has imposed on humanity, and what it means to be a human in the age of AI.

Synthetic Dreams was created using a data collection of 200 million raw images and landscapes around the world. The images incorporate earthly pigments, shapes, and patterns that we associate with our sensory experiences, while paying homage to the Earth’s unbounded poetic sublimity.
title: Synthetic Dreams

description:
Silenced, prosecuted, stereotyped, burned as witches, sexualized, body shamed, abused, and discriminated against for centuries, women are now writing their own history where the future is female.

Rebel Society is a limited edition collection of 7,000 female characters created from hand-drawn elements in celebration of all inspiring, badass women.
title: Rebel Society

description:
They are 5,000 algorithmically generated crypto collectible NFTs that have been generated using 192 hand illustrated attributes, spread over 9 traits.

Each one unique all ranging in rarity.
title: Satoshibles

description:
BitAIrt is an exciting novel concept which promises to make art investments possible for everyone and disrupt the traditional art industry. Every digital creation available is authentic and truly unique, signed and issued by our Artificial Intelligence (AI) artist named DeepBlack — which has been made possible by blockchain technology. Mirroring the exclusivity of original non-AI art, each piece of art created retains a unique signature in the blockchain, ensuring that the digital creation cannot be copied.

DeepBlack is our supercomputer which has been extensively trained to generate 100,000 unique creations. Each of them are signed and encapsulated in an ERC-721 token. DeepBlack generates an extensive range of creative styles, from Classicism to Abstract art, through to Baroque and Minimalism.
title: DeepBlack

Budweiser’s first NFT collection—Budverse Cans Heritage Edition—will act as an entry key to the Budverse, unlocking exclusive benefits, rewards, and surprises for all 21+ (or legal drinking age) NFT holders.

Rubber Duck Bath Party is a collection of 10,000 party-loving, dynamic NFTs hand-drawn by Gal Shir. The art of this collection features a colorful, cheeky, and playful style.

Rubber ducks can change their traits over time by attending bath parties!
title: Rubber Duck Bath Party

description:
Lucky Zeros is a collection of 3,333 cute animals with unique traits, characteristics, and dispositions.

The Lucky Zeros project is the inaugural featured collection from Purebase Studios, launched by Purebase resident artist, Lucky.
title: Lucky Zeros

description: Dormant Dragons is a collection of 5,000 pixel-themed dragon NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain ruling the skies of the metaverse. The collection features 6 custom-made legendary dragons. Enter the Dragon Lair deep within Dragon Valley.
title: Dormant Dragons

description:
Castaways is a social island survival sandbox game developed by Branch. Players are rejected from society, castaway to a small remote island where they must work with others to survive. description:
1,989 Sisters is the first NFT collection by artist and fashion illustrator, Blair Breitenstein. Throughout the collection, Blair highlights her 10 favorite iconic fashion prints, each featured on a shirt, pair of sunglasses, or piece of headwear. Each iconic print is rare and will only show up in a total of six Sisters.

1,989 Sisters got its name from the year 1989, when both Blair and her twin sister were born. This collection is meant to celebrate sisterhood—not just familial sisters, but the magic that happens when expressive, diverse women form a community.

description: J48BAFORMS (Pronounced Jabbaforms) is a multifaceted artistic experiment minted on a boutique bonding curve. A series of 4848 Works of art are available at random. J48BAFORMS started with 1000 hand drawn “LEGACYFORMS” produced by the artist, which serves as the foundation for the series.

Each Colorglyph is a colorful version of an Autoglyph. Colorglyphs turn the black elements in an Autoglyph colorful, using hex colors drawn from the address of the Colorglyph’s creator.

Northern Guilds is a fun-first, device-agnostic dungeon crawler blockchain MMORPG by Pixie Interactive. In a modern take on the pixel perfect art style of nostalgic adventure games, players embark on an epic journey into Ragnarok.

Bring your friends into action-packed, real-time combat throughout Midgard. Construct camps, settlements, and towns, levy taxes on your residents and sales tax on your merchants, or live the life of a nomad, only crafting and collecting what you need for battle. description:
Very rudimentary geometric shapes (primitives), when combined and repeated can become astonishingly complex systems. In particular, when they contain themselves, these simple primitives produce an intricacy that is hard to reproduce or explain, but easy to identify. We call them fractals.

Framergence is a generative NFT art experiment. A shape (a line, a curved line, a circle, a star or a triangle) is put together with a set of curated rules, like: “draw a line here and draw another copy of this pattern 3 pixels to the left”. As simple as that, generative art starts to emerge…
title: Framergence

description:
Kindergarten BabyApes is a collection of 10,000 baby apes going to kindergarten on the Ethereum blockchain.

The story of KBA begins with the parents leaving their children to a place where friendship, learning, and childish games take place—the kindergarten. This project is not only making a difference in the digital space, but making an impact in the real world by building schools for children in need. The Kindergarten BabyApes have already funded building two schools and are aiming for even more! The schools will be built by buildOn during 2022 in Nicaragua and Guatemala.

buildOn staff members and community leaders broke ground building the schools in Yahoska Las Victorias, Nicaragua on March 28, 2022, and Sector Tojmax, Guatemala on March 30, 2022. Both schools are complete.
title: Kindergarten BabyApes

Each building is represented by a non-fungible token on the Ethereum blockchain. In BlockCities, you provably own your buildings and the rights to use them in-game. Users build through the “Mystery Machine” which compiles building components on command, creates a token on-chain, and delivers a constructed building as a rare crypto-collectible

This series spawned from a collaboration between Orange Comet and Sir Anthony Hopkins, and marks the two-time Oscar winner’s first NFT collection.

“The blockchain is the new canvas”
– Sir Anthony Hopkins

Generative Burger Club is a collection of randomly generated Burger Town dwellers. The collection features 1,234 unique characters, plus 6 special characters.

description: HyperDragons is a digital collectible game built on the Ethereum blockchain. Players can purchase and trade dragons using ether. Each dragon has its own unique attributes and appearance, such as cuteness or coolness. Furthermore, dragons can represent players and fight in matches, giving a reason for players to carefully train their warrior dragons. Players train their warrior dragons by boosting their hit point, skills, and glory – the three core features that strengthen a dragon.

description:
A trading card game where users own, trade, sell, and battle on the Ethereum blockchain. Mythereum provides an in-game economy using an ERC-20 token called Mythex which can be acquired by winning battles or trading $CARD with other players.

Mythereum $CARD token is a non-fungible token minted in limited amounts and limited editions. First edition, “genesis” cards, are capped to 5000 cards and are the rarest cards available.

Most Mythereum games are played on our private sidechain. Because of this, playing a game of Mythereum is entirely free! Periodic tournaments with real ETH prizes hosted by the Mythereum team and funded by ongoing card sale proceeds. We offer both free-to-play tournaments and paid-entry, and players only need to have a qualified deck to enter.
title: Mythereum Card

description: Casual Sloths is a collection of 4,444 sloths in a state of cryogenic sleep in a cryogen facility on Slothropolis, a city built on a small planet somewhere in the galaxy. The only danger the sloths face comes from failed experiments of Dr. Chockblain, the caretaker of the sloth population. These sloths are cryogenized for Dr. Chockblains big secret mission 100 years from now.

Players can collect resources, perform upgrades and play-to-earn Ethereum and other cryptocurrencies.

description:
Patchwork Kingdoms is a unique and visually striking collection of 1,000 NFTs with a mission to raise funds for schools around the world.

Each Patchwork Kingdom has a world above representing connected schools and a world below representing unconnected schools. The squares in the hidden, pale “reflection” city represent a lack of connectivity contrasted with the “vibrant” connectivity in schools in the upright city. Data, supplied by Giga, a joint partnership between UNICEF and ITU, is the “paint” that data visualization scientist, designer, and artist, Nadieh Bremer, uses to show how many children are still in need of life-changing connectivity.
title: Patchwork Kingdoms

Each one of these curious creatures was generated by a hand-crafted algorithm and then lovingly selected by creator Danil Krivoruchko to join an elite group of 1,000 Grade-A Ksoids, all available to the discerning investor. The first few drops were sold on the NFT marketplace OpenSea, and available in randomly selected packs of 1, 4, and 10.

description:
BakaArts Darius Puia also known as BakaArts is a 3D and 2D digital artist currently based in Germany who specializes in thought-provoking, fictional, dystopian and cyberpunk worlds. His artworks reflect fantastical “possibilities” that open the mind to an interesting future that hints at where mankind could be headed. He does colorful but also gritty artworks inspired by the likes of Akira, Matrix, Ghost in the Shell and Blade Runner.

He has been doing digital artworks for 15 years. He started his art journey on YouTube as a 2D photoshop tutor where he gained an audience of 150,000 subscribers with his Photoshop tutorials which gained millions of views from many new artists hungry to learn. He then continued with 3D Designs on Instagram and Twitter where he is standing at an audience of over 100,000 Followers.

description:
Pixelglyphs, your forever avatars, are a set of 10,000 unique on-chain avatar NFTs created using a cellular automaton. Each Pixelglyph was created at random during the minting process.

Lil’ Glyphs are fully on-chain little Pixelglyphs that pack each item of the original Pixelglyph’s pixel matrix into the first 50 bits of an unsigned 256 bit integer within the NFT smart contract. The result is a unique number that acts as the Lil’ Glyph token ID, from which the original pixel matrix can be re-created by looping through the first 50 bits.
title: Pixelglyphs

PECland is a sandbox-style Web 3 social game where players can create rich and personalized outfits, homes, and games, and keep pets without restriction. They can even get married and work in this whimsy world.

PEC Friends, the first NFTs from PECland, feature a collection of 3D avatars on the Ethereum blockchain that can be staked to yield $PEC tokens.

description:
PunkBabies are the illegitimate offspring of the OG Punks. Punks hooked up and attributes were mixed – producing 3840 unique human PunkBabies. Aliens, Apes and Zombies were paired up for breeding – producing an additional 60 PunkBabies. Finally one Alien was blessed with a child by immaculate conception!

Each PunkBaby also has a unique shirt color. The RGB color code of which is derived from it’s parents names by merging their respective 4 digit name and converting the resultant 8 digit decimal number to an RGB color code.

Some original attributes have been manipulated for the PunkBabies, e.g. a thermometer replaces a cigarette and mustaches are milk instead of hair. There are also some new attributes since PunkBabies are no different to real babies – they poo, vomit and get snotty noses!

PunkBabies are not affiliated with or endorsed by LarvaLabs.
title: Punk Babies

description: Skullys are reward-based digital collectibles featuring uniquely designed ghost pirate skulls on the Ethereum blockchain. Collect your favorite Skully and embark on a hunt for the loot. The location-based service (LBS) game allows players the ability to perform geo-flagging tasks to earn booty in the form of PO8 tokens. PO8 tokens can be redeemed for additional game accessories to unlock new powers, increasing the earning potential of each individual Skully. Geo-flagging is a feature allowing players to use real-time geo-data from a mobile device or computer to “check in” at various locations such as restaurants, coffee shops, stores, concerts, or anywhere on the go. Players are allowed a minimum of 3 times per day to geo-flag, and each flag pin must occur outside a 800m radius from the latest pin. The higher in ranking the Skullys moves up, the more geo-flagging opportunities will be available within a wider geographic area.

description:
For creators, Unlock provides simplicity. Unlock gives them a JavaScript snippet which lets creators embed locks on their own websites that restrict access to people who have the right key. A lock is just an “access control list”: the list of consumers who are allowed to access their creation (because they own a key). It makes adding a membership layer to your website, or even to a single article, just as easy as embedding an ad.

For users, Unlock provides consistency. Up until now, subscriptions have been totally chaotic, with hundreds of different approaches, requiring you to keep a collection of accounts — and passwords! — to access all the things you care about. There’s no intelligent way to connect them together, unless you’re the platform that controls the network. The blockchain allows Unlock and creators to know only who has access to what, and nothing more.
title: FDC 1 Day Key

A lock is just an “access control list”: the list of consumers who are allowed to access their creation (because they own a key). It makes adding a membership layer to your website, or even to a single article, just as easy as embedding an ad.
